label: BODY

text: Purpose
label: BODY

text: The purpose of the proposed rule change is to adopt a fee schedule for the trading of
label: BODY

text: equity securities on the Exchange in connection with XLE. The XLE fee schedule includes
label: BODY

text: transaction fees (execution and routing fees), covered sale fees, and system fees, as well as a
label: BODY

text: market data revenue sharing proposal.  Changes to Appendix A of the Exchange’s fee schedule
label: BODY

text: include permit fees, application fees, and a modified examination fee, as well as the deletion of
label: BODY

text: certain floor-based fees.  All the proposed fees will be assessed on Exchange members or
label: BODY

text: member organizations, which may include Sponsoring Member Organizations,10 (collectively
label: BODY

text: referred to herein as “member organizations”).  Sponsoring Member Organizations are
label: BODY

text: responsible for the fees generated by their Sponsored Participant’s activities.

label: BODY
